8:
Yahweh continues to say, "You people of Israel are my servants;\q2 you are descendants of Jacob, whom I chose;
\q2 you are descendants of Abraham, who I said was my friend.
\q1

11:
It is certain that all those who are angry with you Israelite people will be disgraced.\q2 Those who oppose you will be wiped out;
\q2 they will all die.


\q1

20:
I will do that in order that people who see it will think about it, and they will know and understand\q2 that it is I, Yahweh, who has done it;
\q1 it is what I, the Holy One of Israel, have done.



\q1
